#COVID19 resulted in the worst economic crisis in 90 years. 

2.7 billion workers were affected by lockdown measures &amp; the global economy contracted by 4.3% in 2020. 

@UNDESA projects modest economic growth in 2021. More in latest #WorldEconomyReport: https://t.co/ODBKe9wWrG https://t.co/RqXFe5WQEU

Our world can only get ahead of #COVID19 one way -- together.

