Who should get the #COVID19 vaccines first? 

Prioritising frontline health &amp; care workers and those at higher risk around the world can save more lives.

@WHO explains: https://t.co/6G7jGpAk1v https://t.co/uIoYfZwv2a

Gender equality contributes to lasting peace.

Research shows that women and men experience, engage in and are affected by armed conflict differently.

@UNPeacekeeping describes how these differences can be leveraged to create a more peaceful world. https://t.co/BsV13yLn6Z https://t.co/A5EuLEiqSg

